# Admire Admin Style Guide

This document outlines the styling rules, conventions, and brand guidelines for the Admire Learning Center admin dashboard.

## Brand Colors

### Primary Colors

- **Primary Blue**: `#4f9bff` - Main brand color, used for primary buttons, active states, and important UI elements
- **Primary Blue (Darker)**: `#3b82f6` - Used for hover states of primary buttons
- **Dark Blue Background**: `#0f1a35` - Main background color
- **Medium Blue**: `#172442` - Used for cards and content areas
- **Accent Blue**: `#2a3c7d` - Used for gradients and accents

### Text Colors

- **White**: `#ffffff` - Primary text on dark backgrounds
- **White (70%)**: `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7)` - Secondary text and labels
- **White (50%)**: `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5)` - Tertiary text and placeholders
- **White (10%)**: `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)` - Subtle borders and dividers

### Status Colors

- **Success**: `#10b981` (Green) - For success states and positive indicators

  - Text: `rgba(16, 185, 129, 1)` or `text-green-400`
  - Background: `rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3)` or `bg-green-900/30`
  - Border: `border-green-500/30`

- **Warning**: `#f59e0b` (Amber) - For warning states and cautionary indicators

  - Text: `rgba(245, 158, 11, 1)` or `text-amber-400`
  - Background: `rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3)` or `bg-amber-900/30`
  - Border: `border-amber-500/30`

- **Error**: `#ef4444` (Red) - For error states and negative indicators

  - Text: `rgba(239, 68, 68, 1)` or `text-red-400`
  - Background: `rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3)` or `bg-red-900/30`
  - Border: `border-red-500/30`

- **Info**: `#3b82f6` (Blue) - For informational states
  - Text: `rgba(59, 130, 246, 1)` or `text-blue-400`
  - Background: `rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3)` or `bg-blue-900/30`
  - Border: `border-blue-500/30`

## Glass Morphism Effects

Glass morphism is a key visual element of our admin dashboard, creating a modern, layered interface with depth.

### Backdrop Blur

- **Light Blur**: `backdrop-blur-sm` - Used for cards and header elements

  - Example: `bg-[#172442]/90 backdrop-blur-sm`

- **Heavy Blur**: `backdrop-blur-md` - Used for modal overlays and dropdowns
  - Example: `bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md`

### Transparency Levels

- **High Transparency**: `bg-white/5` (5% opacity) - Subtle highlights
- **Medium Transparency**: `bg-white/10` (10% opacity) - Card backgrounds, hover states
- **Low Transparency**: `bg-white/20` (20% opacity) - Active elements, buttons
- **Background Overlay**: `bg-[#172442]/90` (90% opacity) - Semi-transparent card backgrounds

## Borders and Dividers

### Border Styles

- **Subtle Borders**: `border border-white/10` - Used for cards and containers
- **Medium Borders**: `border border-white/20` - Used for interactive elements
- **Status Borders**: `border border-green-500/20` - Used for status indicators with respective colors

### Border Radius

- **Small Radius**: `rounded-md` - Used for buttons and small elements
- **Medium Radius**: `rounded-lg` - Used for cards and containers
- **Large Radius**: `rounded-xl` - Used for main sections and feature cards
- **Full Radius**: `rounded-full` - Used for avatars, badges, and circular UI elements

## Shadows and Glows

### Box Shadows

- **Regular Shadow**: `shadow-lg` - Standard shadow for elevated elements
- **Colored Shadow**: `shadow-lg shadow-[#4f9bff]/30` - For primary buttons and active states

### Glow Effects

- **Subtle Glow**: `bg-blue-500/20 rounded-full blur-2xl` - Ambient glow behind elements
- **Accent Glow**: `bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] animate-pulse` - Animated background glow
- **Intense Glow**: `bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl` - Larger area glow

## Animations and Transitions

### Animation Types

- **Pulse**: `animate-pulse` - Used for indicators and subtle attention-grabbing elements
- **Ping**: `animate-ping` - Used for notifications and alerts
- **Float**: Custom keyframe animation for background particles

### Transition Effects

- **Standard Transition**: `transition-all duration-300` - Used for most interactive elements
- **Quick Transition**: `transition-all duration-200` - Used for small UI elements
- **Hover Scale**: `hover:scale-[1.02]` - Subtle scaling effect on hover

## Layout Spacing

### Padding

- **Card Padding**: `p-6` - Standard padding for cards and containers
- **Button Padding**: `px-4 py-2` - Standard padding for buttons
- **Section Padding**: `p-3` - Used for smaller interactive elements
- **Content Areas**: `p-8` - Used for larger content areas

### Margins and Gaps

- **Standard Gap**: `gap-4` - Used between related elements
- **Section Gap**: `gap-6` - Used between sections
- **Vertical Spacing**: `space-y-6` - Standard spacing between stacked elements

## Typography

### Font Family

- Default sans-serif font: Geist Sans
- Monospace font: Geist Mono

### Font Sizes

- **Headings**:

  - H1: `text-3xl font-bold`
  - H2: `text-2xl font-bold`
  - H3: `text-xl font-bold`
  - H4: `text-lg font-semibold`

- **Body Text**:
  - Regular: `text-base`
  - Small: `text-sm`
  - Extra small: `text-xs`

### Font Weights

- **Bold**: `font-bold` - For headings and important text
- **Semibold**: `font-semibold` - For subheadings
- **Medium**: `font-medium` - For emphasis
- **Regular**: Default weight

